        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Saurians make their homes on the sides of tropical volcanoes or tropical mountains. Though they respect all life, saurians consider themselves the protectors of primordial creatures and defend them violently when the need arises. <br/><br/>Saurians stand 20 feet tall and weigh 8,000 pounds."
        }
    ],
